<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>رأيت ابن عمر خلع نعليه <span class="c2">(فجعلهما)</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span> خلفه <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
